text: Ishkarovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Ishkarovsky Selsoviet, Ilishevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 576 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Verkhneyarkeyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ilishevsky District
title: Ishkarovo
